
This game requires:

    o SDL 1.2 		http://www.libsdl.org/
    o SMPEG >= 0.4.4 	http://www.lokigames.com/

1) Run the configure script, see ./configure --help for options.

	$ sh ./configure

2) Build and install the game. The documentation as well as the
   default data files are installed in <prefix>/share.

	$ make depend
	$ make
	# make install

Please report any bug to <agar at csoft dot org>.

